        Type Parameters:
        T - Type of connections created by the passed ConnectionFactory.
        Parameters:
        eventPublisher - A stream of ServiceDiscovererEvents which the LoadBalancer can use to connect to physical hosts. Typically generated from a ServiceDiscoverer.
